data.description: Original Royal Gorge Ranch Homestead established in 1910; within minutes of town with stunning Views!! This 48-acre parcel has original wood accents and walls, original granite fireplace, multiple out buildings, livestock stables, chicken coop, root cellar, and guest cottage. This retreat style property has two gated entrances nestled off of County Road 9. Property backs to BLM land, has natural quartz and fossils throughout, along with a domestic well. This is the perfect property to retreat and enjoy all Canon City has to offer.
